cc:Work.dc:title: Christmas Bells - Coloring Book Page
cc:Work.dc:description:
These Christmas bells and Holly were colored to be entered into the coloring book competition and to show others how easily these coloring book pages can be colored through the use of Inkscape found at inkscape.org.
Please follow along this tutorial and color a coloring page on your own by watching the tutorial at 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JLQ5C4GU has
Also see other tutorials at my website http://www.simpletutorials.net
